Through this project, I learned:

* Data cleaning and preprocessing techniques.
* Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) using visualization tools.
* Building and training a Linear Regression model.
* Evaluating machine learning models using performance metrics.
* Understanding the relationship between advertising spend and sales.
* Applying Machine Learning to solve real-world business problems.

